{"tid":1803503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方預約仇栩欣明早十一點前往北角警署就襲警罪拘捕","createTime":"2019-12-30T08:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T11:00:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b8de547bdaf810388a4afe3fc01cf7c3fc9b5f58","tid":1803503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"城市花園 仇栩欣 Jocelyn Chau<br />\n&middot; 2 mins &middot; <br />\n <br />\n【上任前夕】<br />\n<br />\n阿欣早前收到警方電話，警方決定預約阿欣於明早十一點（12月31日）前往北角警署，並就8月11日晚發生的公眾事件正式控告阿欣襲警罪。<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月1日是新一屆區議會任期正式開始的日子，阿欣會無懼政治打壓，承諾竭盡所能服務城市花園區的街坊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/483780698831135/posts/596944034181467/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F483780698831135%2Fposts%2F596944034181467%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=6ab8d49f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/483780698831135/posts/596944034181467/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"bfa73db7e3cfab057ceaccb81f1c9243d15ea20a","tid":1803503,"uid":305536,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功)<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=cb907de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a><br />\n2. deadline 30/12 (成功)<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=77baab16\" data-aut